# ========================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ========================================
#
# 1. STRIPE SETUP:
#    - Create account at stripe.com
#    - Create products and prices in Dashboard
#    - Set up webhook endpoint: /api/payment/webhooks/stripe
#    - Listen for events: checkout.session.completed, customer.subscription.*, invoice.*, charge.refunded
#
# 2. PAYPAL SETUP:
#    - Create account at developer.paypal.com
#    - Create application in Dashboard
#    - Create subscription plans via API or Dashboard
#    - Set up webhook for: /api/payment/webhooks/paypal
#
# 3. APPLE APP STORE SETUP:
#    - Configure In-App Purchases in App Store Connect
#    - Set up App Store Server Notifications: /api/payment/webhooks/apple
#    - Generate shared secret for receipt validation
#    - Create App Store Server API key for enhanced features
#
# 4. GOOGLE PLAY SETUP:
#    - Configure In-App Products in Google Play Console
#    - Create service account with Google Play Android Developer API access
#    - Set up RTDN topic and subscription
#    - Configure webhook endpoint: /api/payment/webhooks/google
#
# ========================================
